		<descript>
			<abstract>New York City Mobile Telecommunications Franchise Pole Reservation Locations, 2026 is a point representing approximate locations of street light poles, traffic light poles and utility poles reserved by companies authorized by the New York City Department of Information Technology and Telecommunications for the potential installation of mobile telecommunications equipment as of 2026.  This data set was created by NYC Department of Information Technology and Telecommunications and was downloaded from the NYC Open Data website at https://data.cityofnewyork.us/City-Government/Mobile-Telecommunications-Franchise-Pole-Reservati/tbgj-tdd6/about_data in March of 2026.</abstract>
			<langdata>eng</langdata>
